684
00:31:28,860 --> 00:31:29,900
Tomorrow,

685
00:31:32,650 --> 00:31:33,610
I'll come see you.

686
00:31:34,200 --> 00:31:35,150
Okay.

687
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:37,020
Get back to work.

688
00:31:38,040 --> 00:31:39,630
Don't forget to come tomorrow.

689
00:31:40,920 --> 00:31:42,200
I miss you.

690
00:31:44,720 --> 00:31:46,080
I miss you too, Mom.

691
00:31:47,280 --> 00:31:48,920
